{"tid":2090832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊雪盈: 已聯絡愛爾蘭大使館為愛爾蘭女手足提供幫忙","createTime":"2020-07-02T11:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T13:06:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d7c471d800b8f7abe0f1c8c6cba017d47ed4b51b","tid":2090832,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:01:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/clarisseysy/photos/a.918827314858615/4006360592771923/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fclarisseysy%2Fphotos%2Fa.918827314858615%2F4006360592771923%2F&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8BjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=71848ce3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/clarisseysy/photos/a.918827314858615/4006360592771923/</a><br />\n<br />\n楊雪盈 Clarisse Yeung<br />\n&middot; 1 hr &middot; <br />\n <br />\n今日第四站，是灣仔警總。收到消息指昨天被捕的愛爾蘭女手足，沒有足夠的保釋金，我們立即前去幫忙，成功將她保釋出來，也為她購置了衣服。<br />\n<br />\n我們已聯絡愛爾蘭大使館，為她提供幫忙，我們也聯絡了律師協助她。可幸這位女手足的朋友今午也到來了，不用在外地孤零零一個面對。<br />\n<br />\n仍在為其他被捕人士提供協助，有需要的朋友請聯絡我們🙏🏻"},{"pid":"d6004a9c809bd7d57437be04b149fcf8ae12622b","tid":2090832,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c4b0a21531eb94212045d5ea09e31894b760a7","tid":2090832,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:07:28.000Z","msg":"我今日仲諗會唔會無人幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />放心啦"},{"pid":"751fa4ea51831e521cacc8edc462c647b997d43e","tid":2090832,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:10:14.000Z","msg":"愛爾蘭共和軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97cfe4765171a9bdf5634a2601f1da4fec95bcc3","tid":2090832,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:10:14.000Z","msg":"愛爾蘭人 thank you"},{"pid":"81a2482f82750d1969315f54aa1485fc54fc9eab","tid":2090832,"uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:11:56.000Z","msg":"應該係佢！！！！<br />\n<br />\n2345 有外籍手足被捕，因為高舉堅持五大訴求標語<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2089436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2089436</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0205f56c3ddcb0ae3f4aa955d72f63d22469dfde","tid":2090832,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 天佑義人"},{"pid":"0ba335b4e5969e3476209e6241ada66f5edaa714","tid":2090832,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b365553307934fd6a78b0cde2fdbf35200c84c5","tid":2090832,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:14:19.000Z","msg":"推上國際，第一日就公然拉外國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n借個位，BNO平權正視聽<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑色五毛分化警告，大量五毛正在用藍絲有BNO、走人對唔住97後割97後等風向進行分化</span></span></strong>，大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n1.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家比人拉過/有小朋友（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）的話就應該即刻走</span></span></strong>，其他人亦應該起碼做好隨時走既準備，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">香港抗爭運動已經由本土抗爭升級為準國際戰爭， 我們能做的十分有限。 相反大家離開或準備好隨時可以離開，則美國及其盟友可以隨時採取行動，對香港進行制裁，令香港達至零經濟活動，攬炒香港經濟， 甚至日後作出軍事行動亦無需擔心誤傷香港人。</span></span></strong> 而且大家亦可用移民理由提取所有資產及強積金進一步<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打擊香港的財政儲備</span></span></strong>。<br />\n而且多人走亦可以起到掩護最需要走既手足，救奶左野手足係目前最重要既事。<br />\n<br />\n2.大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無需擔心藍絲以及黑警移民英國</span></span></strong>，藍絲得兩種a.垃圾b.收成期，a.涯唔到六年移民監b.揾錢唔捨得走/走要承受巨大損失<br />\n<br />\n重點：大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不應該反對平權或推到現階段設立篩選，因為這樣會妨礙奶左野手足逃難</span></span></strong>。反而，大家應該在藍絲移民英國後再篤灰。大家，要記住，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">篤灰係一把藍絲頭上既利劍，一日未入籍一日都嚮度，我就係要佢地嚮英國每一日都擔心比人篤灰，呢樣恐懼作為懲罰先係最大懲罰</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">相比藍絲，反而大家更應該想辦法推動取消侵犯人權者如689、777、鳩融居英權，因為他們可以憑BC一直不居英，不受英國審判，而定居歐洲。<br />\n<br />\n另外是黑警，酷刑罪在英國是具有域外法權的可公訴刑事罪行。所以請蒐集黑警干犯酷刑罪的證據向英國警方舉報，佢地嚮英國定必得到公平審判<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">97後手足唔會被割</span></span></strong>，首先，佢地可以跟BNO父母及配偶前往英國。第二，對於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">未受BNO平權保障嘅人佢哋仲有美國既救生艇計劃</span></span></strong>，該計劃估計幾日內亦會通過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望樓主可以pin，一齊擊退五毛</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"758bc4f06fd5bf8457b5ebd2afeaf1dde3c00578","tid":2090832,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81a2482f82750d1969315f54aa1485fc54fc9eab","tid":2090832,"uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:11:56.000Z","msg":"應該係佢！！！！<br />\n<br />\n2345 有外籍手足被捕，因為高舉堅持五大訴求標語<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2089436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2089436</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"34d0739193763884b08fa6eff45c58fe67866f7b","tid":2090832,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340655428cc7f9f29950b2a8139d09e98849dff3","tid":2090832,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:27:39.000Z","msg":"西方國家列香港旅遊警示啦"},{"pid":"323dc9268e1d04e5c7d345b0c447b4fb0f20cb8b","tid":2090832,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:28:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8e3ed44967dadf216c04a198f1c572974d85c0","tid":2090832,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:29:07.000Z","msg":"愛爾蘭人，反抗運動師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9bdd7c42f955977a10302bb78d604390d992393","tid":2090832,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"751fa4ea51831e521cacc8edc462c647b997d43e","tid":2090832,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:10:14.000Z","msg":"愛爾蘭共和軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:30:26.000Z","msg":"vpn?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家有國安法"},{"pid":"b4d486d12a5d58f5801744cb89e30443c40805f7","tid":2090832,"uid":284429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img